88
00:06:15,274 --> 00:06:17,469
- [Woman] I'll pay for him.
- What?

89
00:06:18,111 --> 00:06:20,409
No, no. You don't have to do that.

90
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,038
Don't worry about it.

91
00:06:27,887 --> 00:06:30,515
One lucky guy.

92
00:06:30,590 --> 00:06:32,319
No, really. It's my fault.

93
00:06:32,392 --> 00:06:34,383
It's all right. I paid, didn't I?

94
00:06:35,061 --> 00:06:36,619
Here you go. Thank you very much.

95
00:06:46,305 --> 00:06:48,239
Thank you.

96
00:06:48,307 --> 00:06:51,743
