121
00:08:16,195 --> 00:08:17,253
Impugned?

122
00:08:19,465 --> 00:08:21,797
Well, I wouldn't want you
to feel impugned.

123
00:08:46,926 --> 00:08:52,228
So... if you take the same train
tomorrow, I'll pay you back.

124
00:08:55,167 --> 00:08:57,158
It's a date.

125
00:09:06,579 --> 00:09:08,046
[Chattering]

126
00:09:08,114 --> 00:09:09,809
Morning.

127
00:09:09,882 --> 00:09:13,079
- Hey.
- What up, Chaz?

128
00:09:13,152 --> 00:09:16,144
Ooh, yo, I got a good one for you.

129
00:09:16,222 --> 00:09:18,918
Seven players, 40-plus home runs,

130
00:09:18,991 --> 00:09:21,721
with 11 letters in their last names.

131
00:09:21,794 --> 00:09:25,025
- Yastrzemski.
- Yastrzemski.

132
00:09:25,097 --> 00:09:27,361
- You got to spell that for me.
- Morning, Charles.

133
00:09:27,433 --> 00:09:32,496
Y-A-S-T-R-Z-E-M-S-K-I.

134
