Barry, I need a cash check.

135
00:09:34,707 --> 00:09:35,901
How much and what for?

136
00:09:35,975 --> 00:09:38,569
12,000. Location fee
for the Amerispend One shoot.

137
00:09:38,644 --> 00:09:41,135
[Barry] Don't forget to sign
the receipt this time.

138
00:09:41,213 --> 00:09:44,182
- For you, Barry, I'll sign it in blood.
- [Barry] Heard that.

139
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:46,480
OK, that's one. I need six more.

140
00:09:46,552 --> 00:09:48,042
Um... [clicks tongue]

141
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:50,452
- Petrocelli.
- Petrocelli?

142
00:09:50,523 --> 00:09:53,720
- Oh, Charles. Eliot's looking for you.
- P-E-T-R-O...

143
00:09:54,327 --> 00:09:57,626
Oh, come on, yo.
That's only ten letters.

144
00:09:57,697 --> 00:09:59,028
What else you got?

145
00:09:59,098 --> 00:10:02,192
Come on, Chaz,
you got 'em all last week. I need this.

146
00:10:02,268 --> 00:10:03,599
Oh, gee.

147
00:10:03,669 --> 00:10:06,900
All right, Winston,
any of these guys National Leaguers?

148
00:10:06,973 --> 00:10:10,431
I thought it was Major League or Minor
League. What's the National League?

149
00:10:10,509 --> 00:10:13,342
- You don't follow baseball?
- No. Hockey's my game.

150
00:10:13,412 --> 00:10:16,176
- More gore, less bore.
- Where'd you get the questions from?

151
00:10:16,248 --> 00:10:17,772
This cop I know gives 'em to me.

152
00:10:17,850 --> 00:10:19,317
Actually, he's like my uncle.

153
00:10:19,385 --> 00:10:21,410
He's obsessed. Loves challenging me.

154
00:10:21,487 --> 00:10:23,717
Said if I get it right, I get 100 bucks,

155
00:10:23,789 --> 00:10:25,689
and you know I gots
to make that money.

156
00:10:25,758 --> 00:10:27,692
Wait. You don't know the answers?

157
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,990
No. Duh.
That's why I come to you, Chaz.

158
00:10:30,062 --> 00:10:31,495
[Whistles]

159
00:10:31,564 --> 00:10:33,054
Where you been? You're late.

160
00:10:33,132 --> 00:10:34,895
- Come on.
- Sorry.

161
00:10:34,967 --> 00:10:38,164
This is not a lady
who likes to wait, you know.

162
00:10:39,405 --> 00:10:40,838
Susan.

163
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,271
- Charles.
- Hi.

164
00:10:44,477 --> 00:10:47,071
I guess you're here
to raise our commission, eh?

165
00:10:47,146 --> 00:10:48,704
We have some issues.

166
00:10:48,781 --> 00:10:51,272
We feel like no matter
how much we talk to you,

167
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:54,319
we just don't get heard by you people.

168
00:10:54,387 --> 00:10:56,548
