is a case in point.

169
00:10:56,622 --> 00:10:59,591
We agreed on a strategy.
We signed off on it.

170
00:10:59,659 --> 00:11:01,058
Then what happened?

171
00:11:02,328 --> 00:11:05,729
You went off
in all these other directions.

172
00:11:05,798 --> 00:11:08,961
