like how we said it should be.

173
00:11:09,035 --> 00:11:11,663
Look, Susan, the directions
I took were, you know...

174
00:11:11,737 --> 00:11:14,900
I've been doing this for ten years, OK?

175
00:11:20,713 --> 00:11:21,702
I'm sorry.

176
00:11:23,382 --> 00:11:25,680
I'll do it however it is
you want it done.

177
00:11:27,286 --> 00:11:28,947
The time for apologies is over.

178
00:11:29,021 --> 00:11:31,285
What we need now is change.

179
00:11:34,126 --> 00:11:35,889
You don't want me on the account?

180
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:41,261
Uh, Susan appreciates all you've done.

181
00:11:41,333 --> 00:11:43,130
You have different visions.

182
00:11:52,244 --> 00:11:54,235
<i>[Phone rings]</i>

183
00:11:58,417 --> 00:12:00,408
