Get a new account, get back
on your feet, back to what you do best.

189
00:12:17,636 --> 00:12:19,661
Goddamn it.

190
00:12:19,739 --> 00:12:22,936
Talk to me, tell me what's going on,
maybe I can help.

191
00:12:23,008 --> 00:12:24,805
Impugned.

192
00:12:24,877 --> 00:12:26,936
That's a word, isn't it?

193
00:12:29,081 --> 00:12:30,810
[Sighs]

194
00:12:30,883 --> 00:12:32,373
<i>[Rap music playing on stereo]</i>

195
00:12:32,451 --> 00:12:33,440
[Dog barking]

196
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:36,488
[Charles] Shut up, Bernie.
I live here. Amy, please!

197
00:12:36,555 --> 00:12:39,023
- [Barking]
- Bernie, cut it out.

198
00:12:39,091 --> 00:12:40,353
[Whining]

199
00:12:40,426 --> 00:12:43,293
- You're late.
- Sorry.

200
00:12:43,362 --> 00:12:45,193
How was work?

201
00:12:45,264 --> 00:12:47,994
