when I stray from the lesson plan.

207
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,975
There's a lot of that going around.

208
00:13:03,048 --> 00:13:04,208
So, what did I do?

209
00:13:04,283 --> 00:13:07,081
Handed out an English composition
in the math hour today.

210
00:13:07,153 --> 00:13:08,916
He chew you out in front of the kids?

211
00:13:08,988 --> 00:13:12,719
The title for the composition
was "Why We Like Principal Jeffries."

212
00:13:12,792 --> 00:13:14,225
[Car horn honks]

213
00:13:14,293 --> 00:13:16,818
Uh, Jerry called.
There's a message on the machine.

214
00:13:16,896 --> 00:13:18,158
Where you going?

215
00:13:18,230 --> 00:13:21,666
I have a PTA meeting.
It's been on the calendar for six weeks.

216
00:13:21,734 --> 00:13:23,964
- Right.
- [Bernie whimpering]

217
00:13:24,036 --> 00:13:26,300
Amy needs to be quizzed
for her history test,

218
00:13:26,372 --> 00:13:28,340
and Bernie needs to pee.

219
00:13:29,809 --> 00:13:32,300
[Bernie groaning]

220
00:13:33,913 --> 00:13:35,904
Name the act that banned alcohol.

221
00:13:35,981 --> 00:13:37,846
<i>- [rock music playing]
- Volstead Act.</i>

222
00:13:37,917 --> 00:13:40,044
