- 1919.

223
00:13:40,119 --> 00:13:42,610
- Huh?
- 1919.

224
00:13:42,688 --> 00:13:46,818
Yeah. Do you think we can turn
this down a notch below deafening?

225
00:13:47,993 --> 00:13:49,255
Amy!

226
00:13:50,996 --> 00:13:52,054
OK.

227
00:13:53,299 --> 00:13:55,096
