229
00:14:02,074 --> 00:14:04,406
How long...?

230
00:14:14,353 --> 00:14:16,048
<i>[Rock music playing]</i>

231
00:14:16,121 --> 00:14:19,454
- How long did Prohibition last?
- Fourteen years.

232
00:14:44,516 --> 00:14:46,677
[Door opens]

233
00:14:46,752 --> 00:14:48,379
[Door closes]

234
00:14:48,454 --> 00:14:50,445
[Charles cries softly]

235
00:16:16,141 --> 00:16:17,209
[Train's whistle and bell]

236
00:16:17,309 --> 00:16:18,367
[Train's whistle and bell]

237
00:16:26,618 --> 00:16:28,415
