240
00:16:31,757 --> 00:16:33,247
Yeah, right. Gimme my money.

241
00:16:33,325 --> 00:16:34,986
Really. I did.

242
00:16:36,729 --> 00:16:39,527
- Is that your daughter?
- Yeah.

243
00:16:39,598 --> 00:16:42,158
- Amy.
- Oh.

244
00:16:42,234 --> 00:16:44,099
Mine's a few years younger.

245
00:16:44,169 --> 00:16:47,036
- What's her name?
- Amber.

246
00:16:49,975 --> 00:16:52,705
- Oh, she's adorable.
- Yeah.

247
00:16:52,778 --> 00:16:55,406
They make it all worth it, don't they?

248
00:17:08,861 --> 00:17:10,294
Nice briefcase.

